| `salons/{salonId}` | id, salonId, name, phone, address, ownerUid, ownerName, ownerEmail, currencyCode, isActive, timestamps | `location` (lat/lng), `logoUrl` |
| Employees | id, salonId, optional uid, name, email, phone, role, rates, isActive, timestamps | `profileImageUrl` |
| Services | id, salonId, name, serviceName, description, price, durationMinutes, category, isActive, timestamps | — |
| Sales | lineItems[], serviceNames, subtotal/tax/discount/total, employeeId/barberId, paymentMethod, status, soldAt, customerId, report fields, timestamps | — |
| Bookings | salonId, barberId, customerId, startAt/endAt, status, optional service fields, report fields, timestamps | `price` on booking doc if product requires it |
| Attendance | workDate, checkInAt/checkOutAt, presence status, approval workflow fields, timestamps | GPS `location` map |
